Jan 19 (Reuters) - Hangzhou Binjiang Real Estate Group Co Ltd:
* SAYS ITS CONSORTIUM WINS TWO LAND SITES FOR A COMBINED 458.14 MILLION YUAN ($71.61 million) Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/2BfxlgR Further company coverage: ($1 = 6.3981 Chinese yuan renminbi) (Reporting by Hong Kong newsroom)
